Params: {1: '1', 2: 'Selena', 3: 'I suppose the ripples this art piece is trying to create are not what it appears on the surface...', 4: '1'}
{3: 'It has been more than ten minutes since you and Selena unwrapped the box, and you have been trying to understand what you are looking at to no avail.'}
{3: 'Objectively, it is a piece of craftwork made with twisting copper wires, but the chaotic shape has made it very difficult to decipher what the artist wants it to represent.'}
{2: 'Selena', 3: 'My apologies, Commandant. It appears that my understanding of art is still lacking.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Uh... Perhaps it represents how chaotic the universe is?', 3: '11'}
{2: 'Selena', 3: '"All that is transitory is but a metaphor."', 4: '1'}
{2: 'This awkward extruded part is actually supporting the structure above.', 3: '14'}
{2: 'Does this standing pole form a rest sign with the jumbled wires above?!', 3: '16'}
{2: 'Selena', 3: '"The night is long that never finds the day."', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Selena', 3: 'Indeed, what we see to be true might not be the truth.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Selena', 3: "Thank you, Commandant. I'll remember to look at the world from more perspectives.", 4: '1'}
